{"tid":591893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來著住校服扑野真係一種情趣","createTime":"2018-03-14T00:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T10:18:20.000Z","uid":11354,"like":1964,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"17a4c96188a11a3c178b359e71bcecf620f16914","tid":591893,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:19:44.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左三年 <br />\n扑野方面真係咩花式都玩過哂 <br />\n呢排覺得自己開始無咩想搞佢既衝動 <br />\n<br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <br />\n<br />\n我: 去邊度買校服呀? <br />\n佢: 著番我中學個套囉 <br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀慈幼 <br />\n佢: 嘻嘻 傻豬 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我地就渡過左激情既夜晚 <br />\n詳細唔多講 <br />\n但我覺得我地既關係已經修補左"},{"pid":"32404216dc62c0fb94849311a5aed51debd75724","tid":591893,"uid":89665,"like":202,"dislike":51,"score":151,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"叻喇叻喇"},{"pid":"df4dafc3f7bf0bbbb5cc911ed8a83944453d3a0f","tid":591893,"uid":2040,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec35173b86719609ab4736ff5105f72712794fa5","tid":591893,"uid":17270,"like":248,"dislike":7,"score":241,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:21:23.000Z","msg":"扑多幾次咪又係悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e771f7d0344fe9add1443659d35566144612f6ee","tid":591893,"uid":14208,"like":515,"dislike":2,"score":513,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"96c3d03ec8d11c297d7785d72489acf3adccf88d","tid":591893,"uid":14208,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:23:15.000Z","msg":"Alexbb今次竟然冇飲大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3b03e10fd190c968ef2e616cf024c13b2b8521","tid":591893,"uid":172650,"like":3080,"dislike":19,